00:01:41.651 --> 00:01:47.657 line:90%
THE EAST PALACE

00:01:50.118 --> 00:01:51.036 line:90%
Crown Prince.

00:01:55.040 --> 00:01:59.294 line:90%
That spirit… That spirit took my son!

00:02:00.670 --> 00:02:03.673 line:90%
Your Majesty!

00:02:04.633 --> 00:02:06.134 line:90%
Silence.

00:02:09.721 --> 00:02:11.681 line:90%
Where is His Majesty?

00:02:18.021 --> 00:02:20.774 line:90%
His Highness the Crown Prince
went out alone at dawn?

00:02:20.857 --> 00:02:23.443 line:90%
This will lead to greater chaos.

00:02:23.526 --> 00:02:26.613 line:90%
The court must not be the first
to be shaken.

00:02:26.696 --> 00:02:27.739 line:90%
Chief Royal Secretary.

00:02:28.239 --> 00:02:29.491 line:90%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:02:31.618 --> 00:02:34.537 line:90%
Proceed with the funeral rites at once.

00:02:35.622 --> 00:02:36.539 line:90%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:02:42.671 --> 00:02:43.964 line:90%
Your Majesty.

00:02:45.256 --> 00:02:48.134 line:90%
An incident has befallen the Crown Prince.

00:02:49.260 --> 00:02:50.804 line:90%
Are you aware of it?

00:02:51.471 --> 00:02:52.597 line:90%
I have heard.

00:02:57.686 --> 00:03:01.189 line:90%
And yet, how can you remain
so unperturbed?

00:03:01.272 --> 00:03:02.607 line:90%
You may all withdraw.

00:03:02.691 --> 00:03:05.235 line:90%
-Yes, Your Majesty.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

00:03:08.905 --> 00:03:11.282 line:90%
The Crown Princes are dying
one after another.

00:03:11.366 --> 00:03:15.620 line:90%
By that pond spirit, Jangpyeong,
Yunpyeong, and the current Crown Prince--

00:03:15.704 --> 00:03:17.288 line:90%
That is enough.

00:03:17.831 --> 00:03:19.791 line:90%
There is no such thing as spirits.

00:03:20.291 --> 00:03:24.004 line:90%
How could there be spirits
in our Neo-Confucian royal house?

00:03:24.087 --> 00:03:25.422 line:90%
Have you forgotten already?

00:03:25.505 --> 00:03:29.259 line:90%
Thirty years ago, the Crown Princes died
one after another, just as they do now!

00:03:29.342 --> 00:03:32.554 line:90%
Yes. Thirty years have already passed.

00:03:32.637 --> 00:03:34.806 line:90%
But this is not the same as it was then.

00:03:35.306 --> 00:03:39.185 line:90%
My first and second sons died of illness.

00:03:39.936 --> 00:03:41.479 line:90%
And the third Crown Prince,

00:03:41.980 --> 00:03:44.566 line:90%
being deeply tormented in mind,

00:03:45.483 --> 00:03:47.569 line:90%
chose to take his own life.

00:03:48.153 --> 00:03:54.951 line:90%
Such things as spirits do not exist.
Speak no more of them.

00:03:57.829 --> 00:04:02.333 line:90%
Such talk would do Your Majesty no good,
would it, Mother?

00:04:04.002 --> 00:04:06.838 line:90%
If that is truly how you see it,
Your Majesty…

00:04:09.299 --> 00:04:11.593 line:90%
then just as you always have,

00:04:12.802 --> 00:04:14.971 line:90%
stay as you are and take no action.

00:04:15.847 --> 00:04:19.142 line:90%
I shall see to the safety
of the princes myself.

00:04:19.225 --> 00:04:22.687 line:90%
I shall also find a way
to ward off the spirit!

00:04:30.820 --> 00:04:35.200 line:90%
His Highness the Crown Prince!

00:04:35.992 --> 00:04:38.661 line:90%
Come back to us!

00:04:39.496 --> 00:04:42.332 line:90%
Come back!

00:04:43.625 --> 00:04:46.711 line:90%
Come back!

00:04:48.254 --> 00:04:51.508 line:90%
Alas.

00:04:52.008 --> 00:04:55.428 line:90%
Alas.

00:04:55.970 --> 00:04:59.057 line:90%
Alas.

00:04:59.933 --> 00:05:03.645 line:90%
Alas.

00:05:03.728 --> 00:05:06.773 line:90%
Alas.

00:05:19.661 --> 00:05:22.956 line:90%
Alas.

00:05:23.456 --> 00:05:27.252 line:90%
Alas.

00:05:27.335 --> 00:05:29.045 line:90%
Alas.

00:05:29.129 --> 00:05:30.630 line:90%
Stop the wailing!

00:05:35.844 --> 00:05:36.928 line:90%
Do you all truly believe

00:05:37.011 --> 00:05:41.266 line:90%
that spirits could kill
the sons of the King?

00:05:42.684 --> 00:05:47.438 line:90%
That the late King and I
lost our sons to spirits?

00:05:48.189 --> 00:05:50.692 line:90%
And that the King fears spirits?

00:05:51.693 --> 00:05:55.029 line:90%
What officials or subjects
would ever follow such a king?

00:05:55.113 --> 00:05:57.657 line:90%
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

00:05:58.158 --> 00:06:01.244 line:90%
Mere spirits cannot lay a hand
on the royal bloodline.

00:06:01.953 --> 00:06:05.874 line:90%
No one can threaten the royal authority…

00:06:11.129 --> 00:06:13.047 line:90%
be it human or spirit.

00:06:30.607 --> 00:06:32.525 line:90%
Do you truly believe

00:06:33.026 --> 00:06:35.153 line:90%
the spirits can be subdued by that man?

00:06:35.737 --> 00:06:38.531 line:90%
He is the most renowned shaman
in the capital.

00:07:44.180 --> 00:07:48.393 line:90%
I will eradicate the royal bloodline.

00:08:09.205 --> 00:08:11.457 line:90%
Your Majesty, Prince Yeongan is…

00:08:20.174 --> 00:08:22.343 line:90%
What is the matter now, Prince Yeongan?

00:08:22.844 --> 00:08:23.720 line:90%
Prince Yeongan!

00:08:24.220 --> 00:08:25.513 line:90%
What has happened?

00:08:26.014 --> 00:08:29.350 line:90%
Prince Yeongan has suddenly gone
into a convulsion.

00:08:31.185 --> 00:08:33.855 line:90%
Prince Yeongan.

00:08:37.025 --> 00:08:37.984 line:90%
Prince Yeongan…

00:08:42.405 --> 00:08:43.990 line:90%
Did you see?

00:08:44.073 --> 00:08:45.658 line:90%
Did you?

00:08:46.659 --> 00:08:49.329 line:90%
I will take this one as well.

00:08:51.789 --> 00:08:55.960 line:90%
Prince Yeongan! No! Please, no!

00:08:56.044 --> 00:08:57.170 line:90%
Please stop!

00:09:04.677 --> 00:09:07.555 line:90%
Please save Prince Yeongan, Your Majesty.

00:09:07.638 --> 00:09:11.267 line:90%
I will wipe out every last seed
of the East Palace!

00:09:17.315 --> 00:09:19.817 line:90%
<i>What occurred 30 years ago</i>

00:09:20.360 --> 00:09:22.820 line:90%
<i>is repeating itself within the palace.</i>

00:09:23.363 --> 00:09:25.740 line:90%
<i>Therefore, I need you</i>
<i>to come with me this time</i>

00:09:26.491 --> 00:09:28.659 line:90%
<i>and bring this matter to an end.</i>

00:09:30.286 --> 00:09:35.041 line:90%
This humble monk is old and frail
and can no longer shoulder such a task.

00:09:35.541 --> 00:09:38.669 line:90%
However, there is someone else
who may serve in my stead.

00:09:39.545 --> 00:09:40.630 line:90%
Who is it?

00:09:40.713 --> 00:09:43.007 line:90%
A boy named Gu-cheon.

00:09:45.593 --> 00:09:48.262 line:90%
His mother was a shaman.

00:09:48.346 --> 00:09:50.056 line:90%
When she conceived a child,

00:09:50.139 --> 00:09:53.142 line:90%
the deity she served grew angered
and laid a curse upon her.

00:09:54.894 --> 00:09:59.899 line:90%
<i>In her agony, she threw herself</i>
<i>into the river with her child.</i>

00:10:01.776 --> 00:10:05.071 line:90%
<i>Yet the mother, a shaman, died,</i>

00:10:05.571 --> 00:10:07.949 line:90%
<i>and the child survived.</i>

00:10:08.866 --> 00:10:11.160 line:90%
<i>The child had been underwater</i>
<i>for over 15 minutes</i>

00:10:11.244 --> 00:10:14.122 line:90%
<i>and should not have survived.</i>

00:10:15.081 --> 00:10:17.208 line:90%
<i>Perhaps because he died</i>
<i>and came back to life,</i>

00:10:17.708 --> 00:10:21.295 line:90%
<i>he has seen spirits ever since.</i>

00:10:25.800 --> 00:10:26.926 line:90%
Gu-cheon.

00:10:28.344 --> 00:10:29.971 line:90%
You little rascal, get up.

00:10:30.471 --> 00:10:31.889 line:90%
Get up.

00:10:31.973 --> 00:10:33.975 line:90%
Get up at once!

00:10:34.058 --> 00:10:37.270 line:90%
Come now, get up!

00:10:40.815 --> 00:10:43.359 line:90%
Have you gone senile

00:10:43.443 --> 00:10:45.611 line:90%
in this temple of Buddha
and the Mountain God?

00:10:46.112 --> 00:10:49.907 line:90%
<i>Why do you keep sleeping here</i>
<i>instead of your perfectly good room?</i>

00:10:49.991 --> 00:10:53.703 line:90%
Things come out at night and torment me,
so I sleep here.

00:10:54.203 --> 00:10:56.080 line:90%
For heaven's sake.

00:10:57.123 --> 00:10:58.124 line:90%
Gu-cheon,

00:10:58.624 --> 00:11:00.918 line:90%
someone of high standing
has come to see you.

00:11:01.002 --> 00:11:04.088 line:90%
-Come with me at once.
-No. What would you have me do?

00:11:04.172 --> 00:11:06.424 line:90%
Do not sleep the day away
and earn your keep.

00:11:06.507 --> 00:11:07.967 line:90%
With that one thing you can do--

00:11:08.050 --> 00:11:11.095 line:90%
I told you I truly do not wish
to do such work.

00:11:11.179 --> 00:11:12.472 line:90%
A Buddhist earning his keep?

00:11:12.555 --> 00:11:15.266 line:90%
-What a shameless monk.
-What? Shameless?

00:11:15.349 --> 00:11:18.811 line:90%
Fine. I have been wanting to quit
this shameless monk life.

00:11:24.108 --> 00:11:26.360 line:90%
You do not look well.

00:11:26.444 --> 00:11:28.029 line:90%
Is something wrong?

00:11:29.071 --> 00:11:32.074 line:90%
Worry about yourself.
You look deathly pale.

00:11:32.158 --> 00:11:34.243 line:90%
-Enough.
-What do you want with me?

00:11:34.744 --> 00:11:37.788 line:90%
I heard you can see spirits
and even drive them out.

00:11:37.872 --> 00:11:41.209 line:90%
Good grief,
you must be telling the entire village.

00:11:42.001 --> 00:11:44.378 line:90%
No wonder anyone and everyone
comes to see me.

00:11:44.462 --> 00:11:47.882 line:90%
-Gu-cheon!
-There is a reason spirits torment people.

00:11:47.965 --> 00:11:49.926 line:90%
It is because they did something foul.

00:11:50.009 --> 00:11:52.595 line:90%
Stop bringing me people
who stink of such foul deeds.

00:11:53.471 --> 00:11:55.306 line:90%
Watch your tongue, you rascal.

00:11:58.059 --> 00:12:00.061 line:90%
He says his child is ill.

00:12:00.144 --> 00:12:03.147 line:90%
Afflicted by a spirit,
he is in grave condition.

00:12:04.148 --> 00:12:07.485 line:90%
What does that have to do with me?

00:12:08.444 --> 00:12:10.279 line:90%
Do not summon me over such trifles.

00:12:10.780 --> 00:12:12.406 line:90%
I am going to get some sleep.

00:12:12.490 --> 00:12:13.699 line:90%
Gu-cheon!

00:12:17.119 --> 00:12:17.995 line:90%
What?

00:12:18.579 --> 00:12:21.791 line:90%
Do you see something in me?

00:12:21.874 --> 00:12:23.000 line:90%
Your right hand.

00:12:24.418 --> 00:12:25.628 line:90%
You cannot use it.

00:12:27.088 --> 00:12:28.381 line:90%
Why is that?

00:12:28.464 --> 00:12:30.591 line:90%
You have a bite mark left by a spirit.

00:12:31.092 --> 00:12:33.094 line:90%
Seeing that the flesh tore away,

00:12:33.177 --> 00:12:35.263 line:90%
a spirit of deep resentment
has clung to you.

00:12:36.472 --> 00:12:38.182 line:90%
If only you had lived better.

00:12:38.724 --> 00:12:40.476 line:90%
Even so, it is none of my concern.

00:12:40.977 --> 00:12:42.770 line:90%
I beg your pardon.

00:13:31.235 --> 00:13:32.903 line:90%
I am at the palace.

00:13:39.493 --> 00:13:40.494 line:90%
King…

00:13:43.664 --> 00:13:45.958 line:90%
-You may all withdraw.
-Yes, Your Majesty.

00:13:51.297 --> 00:13:53.424 line:90%
Do you know where this is?

00:13:54.300 --> 00:13:56.552 line:90%
Yes, this is the palace.

00:13:57.053 --> 00:13:58.721 line:90%
It is where Your Majesty resides.

00:13:59.347 --> 00:14:04.060 line:90%
Yes, it is a vast, beautiful,

00:14:05.311 --> 00:14:06.771 line:90%
and opulent residence.

00:14:11.567 --> 00:14:15.196 line:90%
At this pond, the Crown Prince
was bewitched by a spirit and died.

00:14:15.863 --> 00:14:19.033 line:90%
It said, "I will wipe out
every last seed of the East Palace."

00:14:19.116 --> 00:14:23.996 line:90%
Even my one remaining young son
is now on the brink of death. So…

00:14:25.915 --> 00:14:27.792 line:90%
I need you to ward off that spirit.

00:14:29.460 --> 00:14:31.379 line:90%
What is the nature of that spirit?

00:14:31.462 --> 00:14:33.881 line:90%
That is none of your concern.
Can you do it?

00:14:34.465 --> 00:14:37.593 line:90%
Can you find that spirit
and get rid of it?

00:15:02.535 --> 00:15:04.495 line:90%
It is no longer present.

00:15:04.578 --> 00:15:06.038 line:90%
The spirit

00:15:06.914 --> 00:15:08.499 line:90%
has gone elsewhere.

00:15:10.918 --> 00:15:13.087 line:90%
I will have to look
at other places as well.

00:15:22.888 --> 00:15:23.931 line:90%
Wait.

00:15:29.854 --> 00:15:31.272 line:90%
You should stay here.

00:15:31.981 --> 00:15:33.399 line:90%
What do you think you are doing?

00:15:34.734 --> 00:15:38.112 line:90%
If those with strong energy are nearby,
the spirit will flee,

00:15:38.612 --> 00:15:40.197 line:90%
so I will go alone and see.

00:15:44.118 --> 00:15:45.619 line:90%
Do not attempt anything foolish.

00:16:02.762 --> 00:16:05.806 line:90%
That crazy, shameless monk
sold me off to the palace.

00:16:06.932 --> 00:16:09.185 line:90%
I cannot. I must not do this.

00:16:09.268 --> 00:16:12.188 line:90%
No, wait!

00:16:16.233 --> 00:16:19.528 line:90%
The Big Dipper lies that way, so this way!

00:16:26.452 --> 00:16:27.536 line:90%
Good grief.

00:16:41.592 --> 00:16:44.970 line:90%
Well… my stomach hurt, so…

00:16:49.308 --> 00:16:51.227 line:90%
No, seriously…

00:16:53.020 --> 00:16:54.939 line:90%
This is unfair!

00:16:57.024 --> 00:16:59.318 line:90%
I did not choose to enter the palace.

00:16:59.819 --> 00:17:01.862 line:90%
However lowborn I may be…

00:17:08.661 --> 00:17:10.079 line:90%
Mark my words.

00:17:11.330 --> 00:17:13.374 line:90%
If you attempt to flee again…

00:17:15.543 --> 00:17:18.128 line:90%
I will sever both your feet.

00:17:18.963 --> 00:17:22.091 line:90%
If you tell others
that you hunt spirits here,

00:17:22.675 --> 00:17:25.177 line:90%
I will sever your jaw.

00:17:25.803 --> 00:17:29.098 line:90%
If you fail to capture the spirit
and my son is harmed,

00:17:29.598 --> 00:17:32.351 line:90%
I will sever your head.

00:17:34.603 --> 00:17:38.524 line:90%
They say that once you enter the palace,
you leave only in death.

00:17:39.275 --> 00:17:40.609 line:90%
That is what the palace is.

00:17:41.652 --> 00:17:44.071 line:90%
If you wish to leave the palace alive,

00:17:44.822 --> 00:17:47.491 line:90%
then capture the spirit at once
and get rid of it.

00:17:48.409 --> 00:17:51.328 line:90%
If you do so, I will grant you
whatever you wish.

00:17:52.371 --> 00:17:53.497 line:90%
Do you understand?

00:18:00.254 --> 00:18:04.216 line:90%
From this moment on, by royal command,
you are a feng shui master of the palace.

00:18:05.843 --> 00:18:08.429 line:90%
I will assign you someone
who may be of use.

00:18:51.305 --> 00:18:52.848 line:90%
You are hardly recognizable.

00:18:54.850 --> 00:18:56.477 line:90%
It has been ten years.

00:18:57.102 --> 00:19:01.190 line:90%
Do you know why I summoned you?

00:19:01.273 --> 00:19:04.860 line:90%
You must have needed someone trustworthy
to keep a secret.

00:19:07.363 --> 00:19:09.615 line:90%
To save your dying son,

00:19:10.407 --> 00:19:12.743 line:90%
you summoned your daughter,
who was as good as dead.

00:19:15.371 --> 00:19:19.750 line:90%
I see you still carry
what happened to you as a child.

00:19:22.711 --> 00:19:23.963 line:90%
How could that be?

00:19:25.798 --> 00:19:27.800 line:90%
I am only glad

00:19:28.634 --> 00:19:30.344 line:90%
to be of service to you, Father.

00:19:36.433 --> 00:19:39.186 line:90%
<i>I have brought a spirit-catcher</i>
<i>into the palace.</i>

00:19:40.604 --> 00:19:44.233 line:90%
<i>Be my eyes and ears,</i>
<i>and keep watch on him.</i>

00:19:45.859 --> 00:19:49.488 line:90%
<i>Whether to entrust him with the task</i>
<i>or put him to death,</i>

00:19:50.489 --> 00:19:52.658 line:90%
<i>I will decide through you.</i>

00:20:01.375 --> 00:20:02.626 line:90%
Is anyone here?

00:20:10.634 --> 00:20:13.554 line:90%
"Someone who may be of use"?
Who on earth is he assigning to me?

00:20:14.054 --> 00:20:16.056 line:90%
I suppose he will send some fearsome men.

00:20:16.140 --> 00:20:18.600 line:90%
There are fearsome men everywhere.

00:20:19.101 --> 00:20:20.602 line:90%
For heaven's sake.

00:20:21.145 --> 00:20:22.438 line:90%
That shameless monk…

00:20:23.188 --> 00:20:24.398 line:90%
Look here.

00:20:25.899 --> 00:20:26.942 line:90%
Look here!

00:20:27.026 --> 00:20:28.402 line:90%
Damn it.

00:20:30.988 --> 00:20:32.197 line:90%
Who are you?

00:20:32.281 --> 00:20:33.741 line:90%
Why do you not answer?

00:20:34.992 --> 00:20:36.618 line:90%
Why do you open the door without…

00:20:38.912 --> 00:20:41.790 line:90%
His Majesty sent me to assist you.

00:20:42.916 --> 00:20:45.753 line:90%
-What am I to do with someone like you?
-Pardon?

00:20:45.836 --> 00:20:49.339 line:90%
I clearly said to change my room first,
not to send me useless people,

00:20:49.423 --> 00:20:50.591 line:90%
yet he pays no heed.

00:20:50.674 --> 00:20:52.885 line:90%
I have not slept a wink all night.

00:20:52.968 --> 00:20:56.180 line:90%
I am truly at my wits' end!

00:20:57.556 --> 00:21:01.060 line:90%
You lose your temper the moment we meet.
Do you have no manners?

00:21:02.186 --> 00:21:06.148 line:90%
Your quarters were chosen
to avoid prying eyes, so do not complain.

00:21:06.231 --> 00:21:07.149 line:90%
Complain?

00:21:08.275 --> 00:21:09.860 line:90%
Complain? Ridiculous.

00:21:10.360 --> 00:21:11.445 line:90%
Look.

00:21:13.155 --> 00:21:15.365 line:90%
Do you know why there is no one here?

00:21:16.283 --> 00:21:20.537 line:90%
People keep dying here
for no reason, do they?

00:21:20.621 --> 00:21:25.793 line:90%
It is because all the Yin energy gathers…

00:21:28.087 --> 00:21:29.963 line:90%
and things like that come to dwell here.

00:21:30.547 --> 00:21:31.381 line:90%
What?

00:21:33.717 --> 00:21:34.718 line:90%
Ominous.

00:21:35.219 --> 00:21:38.722 line:90%
What exactly is here?

00:21:42.434 --> 00:21:43.602 line:90%
Oh dear.

00:21:44.770 --> 00:21:48.398 line:90%
It must be comforting for you,
seeing nothing at all.

00:21:49.066 --> 00:21:50.609 line:90%
I will just go to sleep.

00:21:52.027 --> 00:21:55.906 line:90%
-One cannot expect courtesy from a brute.
-A brute?

00:21:55.989 --> 00:21:59.201 line:90%
In any case, this is our first meeting.

00:21:59.284 --> 00:22:00.619 line:90%
Let us exchange greetings.

00:22:02.246 --> 00:22:04.206 line:90%
I am Saeng-gang, an inspecting court lady.

00:22:04.706 --> 00:22:07.292 line:90%
They say you handle spirits as a shaman.

00:22:07.376 --> 00:22:09.461 line:90%
A shaman? Nonsense.
I do not even serve spirits.

00:22:09.545 --> 00:22:10.879 line:90%
You are no shaman?

00:22:10.963 --> 00:22:13.590 line:90%
-Then how will you hunt the pond spirit?
-None of your concern, so…

00:22:17.511 --> 00:22:19.263 line:90%
Just do as I tell you.

00:22:21.765 --> 00:22:26.145 line:90%
That thing on the ceiling kept me awake,
so I will sleep for now.

00:22:30.107 --> 00:22:32.359 line:90%
-Much to be done.
-What is the matter with you?

00:22:33.777 --> 00:22:35.070 line:90%
Come out!

00:22:35.154 --> 00:22:36.572 line:90%
There is no time to lose.

00:22:44.204 --> 00:22:46.540 line:90%
He must be the feng shui master.

00:22:47.124 --> 00:22:49.251 line:90%
-Where?
-The one who just passed by.

00:22:50.586 --> 00:22:52.421 line:90%
Walk straight.

00:22:53.630 --> 00:22:55.799 line:90%
You are in the palace
as a feng shui master.

00:22:55.883 --> 00:22:57.593 line:90%
Mind your conduct.

00:22:58.510 --> 00:23:01.471 line:90%
I know nothing about feng shui.

00:23:02.389 --> 00:23:03.557 line:90%
Good grief.

00:23:09.188 --> 00:23:10.272 line:90%
You insolent wench.

00:23:10.355 --> 00:23:13.650 line:90%
How dare you raise your head
and look me in the eye.

00:23:13.734 --> 00:23:15.277 line:90%
Have you no manners?

00:23:19.198 --> 00:23:22.743 line:90%
My apologies, ma'am.
I am a court maid from the inspectorate.

00:23:23.285 --> 00:23:27.164 line:90%
By His Majesty's command, I brought
a feng shui master to Prince Yeongan.

00:23:30.375 --> 00:23:34.630 line:90%
Leave. Her Majesty the Queen Dowager
has ordered that no one be admitted today.

00:23:38.675 --> 00:23:39.676 line:90%
Goodness.

00:23:39.760 --> 00:23:43.222 line:90%
After all that talk about manners,
you came away with nothing but a scolding.

00:23:43.305 --> 00:23:44.473 line:90%
Good grief.

00:23:47.476 --> 00:23:51.521 line:90%
Well, have you had a look around?
No sign of the pond spirit in the room?

00:23:51.605 --> 00:23:54.483 line:90%
How would I know?
It is not as if I can see through walls.

00:23:54.566 --> 00:23:56.109 line:90%
Then what exactly can you do?

00:23:56.193 --> 00:23:57.152 line:90%
Please!

00:23:57.653 --> 00:24:01.615 line:90%
Why are you taking the scolding out on me?
For goodness' sake.

00:24:01.698 --> 00:24:04.326 line:90%
You should at least feel some presence.

00:24:12.668 --> 00:24:14.670 line:90%
His Majesty has sent a feng shui master.

00:24:17.339 --> 00:24:18.966 line:90%
A feng shui master?

00:24:21.093 --> 00:24:23.804 line:90%
What on earth is His Majesty thinking?

00:24:23.887 --> 00:24:26.640 line:90%
It is said that he is staying
in the quarters

00:24:26.723 --> 00:24:28.684 line:90%
at the far east end of the East Palace.

00:24:29.184 --> 00:24:30.310 line:90%
What?

00:24:30.936 --> 00:24:33.522 line:90%
Is that not the place long plagued
by unnatural deaths?

00:24:34.356 --> 00:24:38.986 line:90%
Yes, Your Majesty. It was left vacant
after so many sudden deaths at night.

00:24:42.322 --> 00:24:43.657 line:90%
A feng shui master.

00:24:44.157 --> 00:24:46.702 line:90%
What kind of man is he?

00:24:51.498 --> 00:24:52.791 line:90%
Are you all right?

00:24:58.880 --> 00:25:00.132 line:90%
Have you lost your mind?

00:25:00.215 --> 00:25:03.719 line:90%
You carry a great deal of Yang energy.
A rare constitution, indeed.

00:25:11.727 --> 00:25:14.271 line:90%
His Majesty's judgment must have clouded

00:25:14.771 --> 00:25:17.065 line:90%
to entrust such a task
to someone like you.

00:25:17.566 --> 00:25:20.277 line:90%
He assigned you to me
because His Majesty does not trust me.

00:25:20.360 --> 00:25:21.570 line:90%
I am here

00:25:22.070 --> 00:25:25.365 line:90%
only because he threatened my life.

00:25:25.866 --> 00:25:29.119 line:90%
Damn, that bastard. He locks people up
just because he has some power.

00:25:30.287 --> 00:25:32.122 line:90%
Are you speaking of His Majesty?

00:25:32.748 --> 00:25:34.291 line:90%
-That is high treason!
-What?

00:25:34.374 --> 00:25:36.960 line:90%
I meant Chil-bok
from the temple I lived in.

00:25:38.295 --> 00:25:40.839 line:90%
Heavens. Just my luck.

00:25:43.717 --> 00:25:47.012 line:90%
How long do you intend to keep walking?

00:25:47.512 --> 00:25:49.514 line:90%
Are you out for a stroll?

00:25:51.933 --> 00:25:53.352 line:90%
This will not do.

00:25:53.435 --> 00:25:55.604 line:90%
Let us go to the pond
where the spirit appears.

00:25:55.687 --> 00:25:57.064 line:90%
There is no need.

00:25:57.689 --> 00:26:00.275 line:90%
I got there, and the spirit
had already moved on.

00:26:00.817 --> 00:26:04.154 line:90%
It is not as if spirits are bound
to one place the way gwi-mae are.

00:26:05.405 --> 00:26:06.531 line:90%
Gwi-mae?

00:26:07.574 --> 00:26:08.617 line:90%
What is that?

00:26:09.117 --> 00:26:12.079 line:90%
For goodness' sake. This is so bothersome.

00:26:13.538 --> 00:26:15.999 line:90%
Who would know anything about spirits?

00:26:16.958 --> 00:26:20.837 line:90%
Stop complaining and explain it to me.
I can start learning now.

00:26:22.089 --> 00:26:23.840 line:90%
A gwi-mae

00:26:24.341 --> 00:26:26.843 line:90%
does not come from a human death,
as spirits do.

00:26:27.344 --> 00:26:29.304 line:90%
It forms when sinister forces of nature

00:26:29.388 --> 00:26:33.725 line:90%
or the energy from human ill will
gather in one place.

00:26:33.809 --> 00:26:36.186 line:90%
There was one
on the ceiling of my room earlier

00:26:37.854 --> 00:26:39.231 line:90%
and another one over there.

00:26:43.985 --> 00:26:46.613 line:90%
<i>It has no soul,</i>
<i>so it cannot be driven out like a spirit.</i>

00:26:46.696 --> 00:26:48.407 line:90%
<i>It is more troublesome to handle.</i>

00:26:48.907 --> 00:26:52.035 line:90%
<i>They torment people</i>
<i>with darkness in their hearts</i>

00:26:52.536 --> 00:26:53.787 line:90%
<i>and bewitch them.</i>

00:26:58.708 --> 00:26:59.793 line:90%
Let us go.

00:26:59.876 --> 00:27:01.837 line:90%
It is best to avoid them.

00:27:08.385 --> 00:27:11.304 line:90%
Then is the pond spirit a gwi-mae as well?

00:27:11.805 --> 00:27:14.724 line:90%
Gwi-mae do not hold grudges
against humans.

00:27:14.808 --> 00:27:17.352 line:90%
-It is most likely a won-gwi.
-A won-gwi?

00:27:17.436 --> 00:27:19.896 line:90%
-What is a won-gwi?
-Good grief.

00:27:24.025 --> 00:27:27.737 line:90%
Among the many kinds of spirits,
common-gwi are souls lingering in regret,

00:27:27.821 --> 00:27:29.948 line:90%
unable to pass on to the afterlife.

00:27:30.657 --> 00:27:32.868 line:90%
They cause no real harm.

00:27:33.702 --> 00:27:36.663 line:90%
Won-gwi are the souls of those
who died bearing deep resentment.

00:27:36.746 --> 00:27:40.083 line:90%
They torment the one
who caused their resentment.

00:27:40.167 --> 00:27:42.252 line:90%
As the resentment grows and takes form,

00:27:42.335 --> 00:27:45.505 line:90%
it weighs down the soul
and binds it to the earth,

00:27:45.589 --> 00:27:46.965 line:90%
keeping it from passing on.

00:27:51.136 --> 00:27:53.388 line:90%
Only by getting rid of
that mass of resentment

00:27:54.973 --> 00:27:57.684 line:90%
can the soul bound to the earth
be released to pass on.

00:27:58.685 --> 00:28:00.729 line:90%
And even that will be no easy feat.

00:28:03.607 --> 00:28:07.277 line:90%
The pond spirit…
Prince Yeongan… The pond spirit…

00:28:11.281 --> 00:28:13.950 line:90%
Prince Yeongan
is being tormented by a spirit.

00:28:15.118 --> 00:28:17.829 line:90%
I cannot believe she turned away people
sent by His Majesty.

00:28:18.371 --> 00:28:20.790 line:90%
Does the Queen Dowager
have any sense at all?

00:28:21.291 --> 00:28:23.543 line:90%
Huh? Well, well.

00:28:24.169 --> 00:28:27.547 line:90%
You speak ill of the Queen Dowager?
You said it was treason for me to do so.

00:28:30.926 --> 00:28:34.679 line:90%
More importantly,
why tear up all the perfectly good sheets?

00:28:35.347 --> 00:28:36.473 line:90%
None of your concern.

00:28:38.642 --> 00:28:40.435 line:90%
You seem quite at ease.

00:28:40.519 --> 00:28:43.730 line:90%
We must see Prince Yeongan to banish
the spirit, yet you seem unconcerned.

00:28:43.813 --> 00:28:46.274 line:90%
Of course I am concerned.

00:28:46.358 --> 00:28:50.820 line:90%
If I fail to save the son of His Majesty,
I will be the one to die.

00:28:50.904 --> 00:28:52.531 line:90%
It even leaves me sleepless at night.

00:28:53.031 --> 00:28:54.115 line:90%
What I mean is,

00:28:54.199 --> 00:28:57.619 line:90%
is it not pitiful that the child
is tormented by such a grotesque thing?

00:28:57.702 --> 00:29:00.288 line:90%
I do not even know this child.
Why should it concern me?

00:29:01.915 --> 00:29:03.750 line:90%
How can you think only of yourself?

00:29:04.251 --> 00:29:07.712 line:90%
If you have the time,
look into that pond spirit instead.

00:29:07.796 --> 00:29:10.423 line:90%
Who it was in life
and what grudge it bears.

00:29:10.507 --> 00:29:13.093 line:90%
Only then can I get rid of
the pond spirit.

00:29:13.176 --> 00:29:15.887 line:90%
It will be difficult.
Even if they know, they will not speak.

00:29:15.971 --> 00:29:18.473 line:90%
Then go fetch a peach tree branch.

00:29:18.557 --> 00:29:19.849 line:90%
One that grows eastward.

00:29:21.351 --> 00:29:24.604 line:90%
-What for?
-You never simply say yes.

00:29:26.106 --> 00:29:27.399 line:90%
Fetch it at once.

00:29:30.110 --> 00:29:30.944 line:90%
This man, truly…

00:29:32.988 --> 00:29:35.156 line:90%
Ask again, with proper respect!

00:29:35.824 --> 00:29:37.075 line:90%
Be quick!

00:29:37.158 --> 00:29:39.327 line:90%
Assist me? Nonsense.
She does not know a thing.

00:29:42.789 --> 00:29:45.458 line:90%
Why does it have to be a branch
growing eastward?

00:29:53.383 --> 00:29:55.594 line:90%
Here. This should do, should it not?

00:29:57.053 --> 00:29:59.681 line:90%
I have heard that peach trees
drive away spirits.

00:30:00.432 --> 00:30:01.474 line:90%
Well done.

00:30:03.101 --> 00:30:07.188 line:90%
-How will you ward off spirits with… that?
-Oh, that feels good.

00:30:09.524 --> 00:30:10.984 line:90%
Much better.

00:30:17.782 --> 00:30:21.036 line:90%
-I almost died trying to reach it.
-All this just to scratch your back?

00:30:28.126 --> 00:30:30.128 line:90%
<i>I submit this report to you, Father.</i>

00:30:30.879 --> 00:30:33.173 line:90%
<i>You may set aside your concern</i>

00:30:33.256 --> 00:30:36.468 line:90%
<i>that he might uncover anything</i>
<i>about the pond spirit</i>

00:30:36.551 --> 00:30:39.804 line:90%
<i>because he is doing nothing at all.</i>

00:30:40.388 --> 00:30:43.350 line:90%
<i>He stays in his room all day,</i>
<i>speaking only of sleep.</i>

00:30:52.233 --> 00:30:56.071 line:90%
-Why does this keep happening?
-How many times has this happened?

00:30:56.154 --> 00:30:58.823 line:90%
I know. The rumors of a spirit
in the East Palace seem to be true.

00:30:58.907 --> 00:30:59.991 line:90%
So it seems.

00:31:00.075 --> 00:31:02.369 line:90%
Prince Yeongan cannot take
even rice gruel.

00:31:02.452 --> 00:31:05.288 line:90%
-Exactly. They say he is worse this time.
-Pardon me.

00:31:07.082 --> 00:31:09.125 line:90%
What is going on?

00:31:15.632 --> 00:31:17.717 line:90%
What on earth is happening to him?

00:31:20.553 --> 00:31:22.222 line:90%
-Prince Yeongan!
-What ails him?

00:31:22.305 --> 00:31:24.307 line:90%
Please come to your senses,
Prince Yeongan!

00:31:25.016 --> 00:31:28.144 line:90%
-Do something at once!
-Prince Yeongan.

00:31:28.770 --> 00:31:31.398 line:90%
-Come to your senses.
-Is he truly possessed by a spirit?

00:31:32.649 --> 00:31:34.609 line:90%
What on earth should we do?

00:31:41.324 --> 00:31:42.867 line:90%
Prince Yeongan is gravely ill.

00:31:49.040 --> 00:31:51.501 line:90%
-Already?
-What will you do?

00:32:00.635 --> 00:32:02.053 line:90%
No other choice, then.

00:32:11.146 --> 00:32:13.148 line:90%
What are you going to do with it…

00:32:20.321 --> 00:32:23.158 line:90%
So are you going to Prince Yeongan?

00:32:23.241 --> 00:32:25.118 line:90%
You should stay here. It is not safe.

00:32:31.958 --> 00:32:36.004 line:90%
You never listen, do you?
I told you not to follow.

00:32:36.087 --> 00:32:37.881 line:90%
I said you must go to Prince Yeongan.

00:32:37.964 --> 00:32:40.884 line:90%
That is why I am here.
I am going to Prince Yeongan.

00:32:40.967 --> 00:32:42.510 line:90%
What on earth are you trying to do?

00:32:42.594 --> 00:32:45.847 line:90%
I have no choice
in letting you see me like this,

00:32:45.930 --> 00:32:49.684 line:90%
but you must not tell anyone
what I am about to do.

00:32:54.522 --> 00:32:56.941 line:90%
Why are you putting blood on the branch?

00:32:57.025 --> 00:32:59.611 line:90%
So I may bring it into the other world.

00:33:00.111 --> 00:33:01.571 line:90%
The other world? You mean…

00:33:03.072 --> 00:33:04.199 line:90%
The Realm of Gwi.

00:33:05.992 --> 00:33:06.868 line:90%
The Realm of Gwi…

00:33:06.951 --> 00:33:08.578 line:90%
I may not come out of the water.

00:33:10.580 --> 00:33:13.958 line:90%
-Even then, do not pull me up.
-Are you telling me to let you die?

00:33:14.042 --> 00:33:17.128 line:90%
Yes. That is how I reach the Realm of Gwi.

00:33:19.130 --> 00:33:20.965 line:90%
Oh, right. Since you followed me…

00:33:26.429 --> 00:33:30.600 line:90%
Spirits may be listening.
Come closer so we can speak quietly.

00:33:45.156 --> 00:33:49.536 line:90%
I lack Yang energy, so it would be best
for me to take something of yours.

00:33:57.168 --> 00:33:58.253 line:90%
Well…

00:34:01.172 --> 00:34:02.715 line:90%
You should go now.

00:34:04.300 --> 00:34:06.177 line:90%
Remember what I told you to do.

00:34:08.596 --> 00:34:09.681 line:90%
Look here.

00:37:47.148 --> 00:37:48.566 line:90%
What should we do?

00:37:49.067 --> 00:37:50.943 line:90%
What should we do about this?

00:37:52.570 --> 00:37:54.697 line:90%
-Prince Yeongan!
-Prince Yeongan.

00:38:03.456 --> 00:38:05.333 line:90%
Prince… Prince Yeongan!

00:38:21.849 --> 00:38:25.186 line:90%
<i>"I shall burn your vessel,</i>
<i>shrouded in darkness."</i>

00:38:59.470 --> 00:39:00.763 line:90%
-Your Highness!
-Prince Yeongan!

00:39:00.847 --> 00:39:03.224 line:90%
-Lady Jang, summon…
-Please come to your senses!

00:39:03.307 --> 00:39:05.226 line:90%
-Summon the physician!
-Yes, ma'am.

00:39:31.169 --> 00:39:34.172 line:90%
If Prince Yeongan shows
any signs of waking,

00:39:34.672 --> 00:39:36.799 line:90%
let it see your blood.

00:39:37.383 --> 00:39:38.968 line:90%
<i>The window will be brief.</i>

00:40:33.898 --> 00:40:35.316 line:90%
I knew it would not work,

00:40:35.399 --> 00:40:37.485 line:90%
not knowing the nature of that spirit.

00:40:57.797 --> 00:40:59.340 line:90%
He truly is here.

00:41:11.560 --> 00:41:12.645 line:90%
Who are you?

00:41:13.854 --> 00:41:16.899 line:90%
What grudge drives you
to kill the royal bloodline?

00:44:18.622 --> 00:44:21.917 line:90%
Subtitle translation by: Yun-hee Jang